Title: Hyper Racing Madness
Description:
Hyper Racing Madness takes you at journey of "The Driver" where you drive the wheel of sports cars from multiple top notch car companies, from an entry level car such as the Dodge Challenger, to an expensive super car like the Lamborghini Hurricane.

The player races against artificial intelligence-controlled cars in a 3D environment, with the objective of winning the race and hence obtaining 3 stars in the level. Over the course of the game, the player can gradually unlock access to various new cars, levels, maps, and race modes. Players can also choose to play in a 1-player quick race or challenge a friend in the 2-player mode featured in Hyper Racing Madness.

For "Player A"

Direction Keys-(Up,Down,Left,Right)
Enter- Reset position
Esc- Pause Race

For "Player B"
Direction Keys-(W,A,S,D)
Tab- Reset position
Esc- Pause Race
-------------------
Classic: Cross the finish line first to win.
Escape: Finish the laps before the timer runs out.
Survival: Don't came last when the timer runs out .
Infection: Infected cars have temporary engine boost .

AI-controlled opponents
5 levels with increasing difficulty
5 maps (Rural, Arctic, Desert, Urban, Moon)
5 race modes (Classic, Escape, Survival, Infection, Special)
Unlock able cars and levels
Star rating system in levels
Car rank updated in real-time
Split-screen multiplayer

Title: Kitchen Mahjong

Title: Motoracer vs Huggy

Motoracer vs Huggy is a game in which you have to crush the blue monsters of Huggy that are annoying to many! You will have to do this on a frisky motorcycle, so this is a rather risky activity, but it is fun and driving!

Crush as many blue evil monsters as possible, but try not to crash into their friends, Kisi with bombs, because they will blow you up in the same second! Also watch out for other obstacles such as trees, bushes, cacti and rocks. You can do tricks if you are in the air!

Shoot down Huggy's and dodge Kisi and other obstacles!

A, D - motorcycle turn
Space - rearview mirror
Left Shift - nitro

Title: Wok Planet

Woks lived in harmony with their planet for thousands of years, until uninvited guests appeared on it. The aliens were not very friendly and took over most of the world. Woks who could not hide are sent for experiments. The rest are forced to sit out in caves in anticipation of a miracle. But there are those who are not ready to put up with defeat. They created a resistance and fight back against the aliens.
Become a member of the resistance, collect mechanisms and use the wok's special abilities to take back control of the planet!

Title: Ragdoll Down

An exciting arcade game in which players are given a unique opportunity to inflict maximum damage to ragdoll in various extreme conditions. You'll have to use a variety of objects and environments to accomplish this goal. 

Waiting for you are:

✅ Shop with items

✅ Vivid graphics

High-quality graphics, exciting locations and challenging levels are waiting for you. Enjoy!

- the figure placed in the field changes its color to a lighter one

Do you like the Pacman game style? If yes, this game is dedicated to you.
Avoid the monsters at all costs, collect all the dots to complete a map. Eating a magic potion will help increasing your hero's power and weaken the monsters; During this magic period, your hero can kill the monsters.

Vacuum Rage - a fun arcade game about a crazy vacuum cleaner robot.
There is too much rubbish in this area, we must clean it up. A robot vacuum cleaner is ideal for solving this problem.
Only now the robot has gone crazy and has begun to collect everything that comes in its way, indiscriminately. Real crazy vacuum cleaner rage!

The robot vacuum cleaner has gone crazy, now its only task is to suck up everything that gets in its way. People, trees, houses all go to the landfill, don't miss anything.

- Absorb everything that gets in the way!

Title: Traffic Control Math

Left-click: Select unit/building.
Double left-click: Select all similar units on screen.
Right-click: Issue command (move, attack, gather, etc.).
Click and drag (left button): Draw selection box to select multiple units.
Mouse scroll: Move the camera up, down, left, or right (when the mouse is at the edge of the screen).
Mouse scroll wheel: Zoom in/out.

Objective: The main objective of Feudal Wars is to build a powerful army, expand your territory, and defeat other players to become a dominant force in the game world.

Buildings: Players need to construct various types of buildings that serve different purposes, including resource production, military training, and research facilities. Each building contributes to your economy and army strength.
